                                    ],
                                    "type": "text",
                                    "content": "their methods need to retrieve a very large portion of history conversations to achieve better results than the standard Transformer. In addition, these models still need to concatenate the retrieved raw history conversation text with the current conversation context, yielding concatenations that are still much longer than the 128 token truncation lengths. Therefore, the incorporation of historical contexts in these methods is still limited by the short token truncation lengths of pre- trained models."
