                                    "type": "text",
                                    "content": "In this work, we propose a novel model, namely HAHT, for the MSC task. Figure 2 shows the overall structure of HAHT, which consists of three main components: 1) hierarchical history conversation encoder, 2) history- aware context encoder, and 3) history- aware response generator. We present the details of each component of HAHT as follows."
